article_id:2345,category_name:News,title_name:Part Two of Chapter 20: The Sacred Tree Added to the Main Campaign!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a819c25b50b08333a3de363ec0f53818.png,message:<div>Part two of Chapter 20: The Sacred Tree was added to the main campaign on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626847200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a819c25b50b08333a3de363ec0f53818.png"></div><div><br></div><div>Nedrick speaks of his birth in order to further ascend the Sacred Tree, and his words change Zethia&#39;s heart. Meanwhile, the prince and friends hurry after them to protect the shard, but their path is blocked by the faerie king&mdash;and their battle is then interrupted by an unexpected arrival...</div><div><br></div><div>We hope you&#39;re looking forward to seeing what&#39;s in store for the prince and his friends!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Notes</div><div>1. Part two of chapter 20 of the main campaign will unlock when you clear Ch. 20 / 4-3 &quot;The World He Left Behind.&quot;</div><div>2. The release of part two does not include additional dragons who can be unbound using draconic essences, but you can use the draconic essence icon displayed on the area map for each chapter in the main campaign to check the dragon whose draconic essence you can obtain, how many draconic essences you currently have, how many more you can obtain, and the quests from which you can obtain draconic essences.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1626847200,update_time1626312890